{"tid":1759301,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"無行動，唔代表無野做，全部人即刻開始練體能","createTime":"2019-11-27T14:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T13:21:39.000Z","uid":293677,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"31467635b04484a9e22706dcf3e647f2c15c64c0","tid":1759301,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />是咁的<br />\n古語有云：修身齊家治國平天下<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要做大事，就要先裝備好自己</span><br />\n只係想提醒手足呢場係長期戰爭<br />\n呢場革命運動未完架<br />\n平日要抽時間出黎<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每個香港人都應該要提升自己既體能</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大方向就係：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民運動，全民健身，<br />\n然後全民習武，<br />\n最後達至&quot;全民勇武&quot;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你唔打得 都起碼要跑得<br />\n滅少補擒獲既機會</span><br />\n香港人唔洗服兵役<br />\n長期以來又賤視體育運動科目<br />\n搞到個個體能好差<br />\n上到戰場<br />\n淨係個心勇係唔夠架<br />\n人數再多都係散兵游勇<br />\n<br />\n引用普京一句說話：<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>沒有實力的憤怒是毫無意義的</ins></span></span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申：自知體能太弱，上到戰場只係做炮灰<br />\n小弟從六月已經開始舉鐵，之後買埋奶粉飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共勉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，運動<br />\n香港人，健身<br />\n香港人，習武<br />\n<br />\n講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817a8ba76c001e6d2d84486d97a069f20af6259c","tid":1759301,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4fa0481f3bcbb7cf2c20234919f97a42091eac5","tid":1759301,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"塞爆康文署gym room ?"},{"pid":"427b8441af9ba04dba5ada232d5ad1f8e19ead2e